29:52.660 --> 29:55.940
So it's, you get something that's a little more curated,

29:55.940 --> 29:57.940
a little more polished, a little more like,

29:57.940 --> 30:01.140
yes, we know you're using this as a daily driver,

30:01.140 --> 30:02.540
but with the fresh packages.

