31:08.340 --> 31:10.500
Yeah, and you get a very, at the end of the day,

31:10.500 --> 31:12.420
a very opinionated plasma setup with that.

31:12.420 --> 31:13.740
Like we said, with that global menu,

31:13.740 --> 31:15.940
that top bar based on Wayland,

31:15.940 --> 31:19.220
they use the Nitrix theme, obviously, out of the box.

31:19.220 --> 31:22.020
